content: कुंजः, --जं {@--1@} A place overgrown with plants or creepers, a bower, an arbour; चल सखि कुंजं सतिमिरपुंजं शीलय नीलनिचोलं <ls>Gīt. 5</ls>; वंजुललताकुंजे <ls n="Gīt.">12</ls>; <ls>Me. 19</ls>; <ls>R. 9. 64.</ls> {@--2@} The lower jaw. {@--3@} A cave. {@--4@} A tooth. {@--5@} The tusk of an elephant.
